# Docker Compose: bind host for published ports (API, admin UI, optional arena UI).
# Default 127.0.0.1 — only reachable from this machine.
# Use 0.0.0.0 so Raspberry Pis and other PCs on the pool LAN can connect.
# If you expose 0.0.0.0, use a firewall you trust (pool Wi‑Fi only, etc.).
# POLODECK_BIND_ADDRESS=0.0.0.0
# Default Creds: deckuser:deckMe@4249
# Optional: enable arena static container with the stack (see docs / setup.sh).
# COMPOSE_PROFILES=arena
